text: As AZ works to contain the spread of #COVID19, I’m thankful to @VP for connecting this weekend to offer additional @CDCgov assets. Leadership across AZ continues to protect public health, including @ASU Pres. @michaelcrow’s preparation in returning students to campus this fall. https://t.co/gSkftlwUHy
